  <zone type="main">
    <milestone unit="tei:head" spanTo="#e1-0038.07"/>
    <line rend="center"><hi rend="underline">Act 1</hi></line>
    <anchor xml:id="e1-0038.07"/>
    <milestone unit="tei:stage" spanTo="#e1-0038.08"/>
    <line rend="indent1">Scene -- <add place="superlinear">Night</add> A Ravine of Icy Rocks in
      the</line>
    <line>Indian Caucasus. Prometheus is discovered</line>
    <line>bound to the precipice-- Panthea &amp; Ione</line>
    <line>are seated at his feet.</line>
    <anchor xml:id="e1-0038.08"/>
    <milestone unit="tei:speaker" spanTo="#e1-0038.09"/>
    <line rend="center">Prometheus</line>
    <anchor xml:id="e1-0038.09"/>
    <line>Monarch of Gods &amp; <mod>
        <del rend="overwritten">d</del>
        <add place="intralinear">D</add>
      </mod>&#230;mons &amp; all <mod>
        <del rend="overwritten">s</del>
        <add place="intralinear">S</add>
      </mod>pirits</line>
    <line>But One, who throng those bright &amp; rolling Worlds</line>
    <line>Which Thou &amp; I alone of living things <add><metamark function="separate"
          >&#166;</metamark></add>
      <milestone unit="tei:seg" spanTo="#e1-0038.02" xml:id="e1-0038.04" corresp="#e1-0038.05"/>,
        regard<anchor xml:id="e1-0038.02"/></line>
    <line>Behold with sleepless eyes <add place="superlinear"><metamark function="displacement"
          >&#8629;</metamark></add>
      <anchor xml:id="e1-0038.05"/><anchor xml:id="e1-0038.06"/>
      <milestone unit="tei:seg" spanTo="#e1-0038.03" next="#e1-0038.04" corresp="#e1-0038.06"/> this
      Earth <anchor xml:id="e1-0038.03"/></line>
    <line>Made multitudinous with thy slaves, whom thou</line>
    <line>Requitest for knee-worship, prayer &amp; praise,</line>
    <line>And toil, &amp; hecatombs of broken hearts,</line>
    <line>With fear &amp; self contempt &amp; barren hope;</line>
    <line>Whilst me, whom am thy foe, eyeless in hate,</line>
    <line>Hast thou made reign &amp; triumph, to thy scorn,</line>
    <line>Oer mine own misery &amp; thy vain revenge. . . .</line>
    <line>Three thousand years of sleep-unsheltered hours</line>
    <line>And moments, aye divided by keen pangs</line>
    <line>Till they seem years, torture &amp; solitude,</line>
    <line>Scorn &amp; despair--<del rend="strikethrough">more glorious than thy throne</del><anchor
        xml:id="e1-0038.01"/></line>
  </zone>
